ir John de Thornbury родился около 1350 г. в местности варвиккшир, Англия. Его родителей звали Sir John de Thornbury Sr и Lady Elizabeth Wallace. У него был по крайней мере 1 сын и 1 дочь от Naverina de Knightley. Он умер 4 сентября 1396 г. в местности честиртон, варвиккшир, Англия в возрасте 47 лет и был похоронен в местности литл мунден, хиртфордшир, Англия, Великобритания."},"sm":{"ABT 1350–September 4 1396":"e tusa o le 1350–4 Setema 1396","1325–Female":"1325–Ua Maliu","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1354–1396":"1354–1396","1375–1418":"1375–1418","1396–1457":"1396–1457","–Male":"Ua Maliu","–Female":"Ua Maliu","ABT 1350":"e tusa o le 1350","1457":"1457","1325":"1325","4 September 1396":"4 Setema 1396","September 4 1396":"4 Setema 1396","1354":"1354","1375":"1375","1396":"1396","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1418":"1418","Warwickshire, England":"Warwickshire, Egelani, United Kingdom","Chesterton, Warwickshire, England":"Chesterton, Warwickshire, Egelani","All Saints Churchyard, Little Munden, Hertfordshire, England":"Little Munden, Hertfordshire, Egelani, United Kingdom"},"sk":{"ABT 1350–September 4 1396":"okolo 1350–4. september 1396","1325–Female":"1325–Zosnulá","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1354–1396":"1354–1396","1375–1418":"1375–1418","1396–1457":"1396–1457","–Male":"Zosnulý","–Female":"Zosnulá","ABT 1350":"okolo 1350","1457":"1457","1325":"1325","4 September 1396":"4. september 1396","September 4 1396":"4. september 1396","1354":"1354","1375":"1375","1396":"1396","1350":"1350","1382":"1382","1418":"1418","Warwickshire, England":"Warwickshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Chesterton, Warwickshire, England":"Chesterton, Warwickshire, England","All Saints Churchyard, Little Munden, Hertfordshire, England":"Little Munden, Hertfordshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo"},"es":{"ABT 1350–September 4 1396":"aproximadamente 1350–4 de septiembre de 1396","1325–Female":"1325–Fallecida","1350–1396":"1350–1396","1354–1396":"1354–1396","1375–1418":"1375–1418","1396–1457":"1396–1457","–